## Files to update in your repo:
1. Replace `.github/workflows/ci-cd.yml` with the new one
2. Replace `docker-compose.prod.yml` with the new one
3. Replace `nginx/nginx.conf` with the new one

## GitHub Secrets to add:
| Secret | Value |
|--------|-------|
| `DEPLOY_HOST` | new EC2 Elastic IP |
| `DEPLOY_USER` | `ubuntu` |
| `DEPLOY_SSH_KEY` | contents of `facidance-key.pem` |
| `AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID` | same IAM user as Facidance |
| `AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY` | same |
| `AWS_SG_ID` | new EC2 security group ID |
| `DATABASE_URL` | `postgresql://postgres:PASSWORD@postgres:5432/bikersstudio` |
| `POSTGRES_DB` | `bikersstudio` |
| `POSTGRES_USER` | `postgres` |
| `POSTGRES_PASSWORD` | a strong password |
| `NEXTAUTH_URL` | `https://bikerstudio.facidance.online` |
| `NEXTAUTH_SECRET` | random string |
| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID` | your value |
| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET` | your value |
| `RAZORPAY_KEY_ID` | your value |
| `RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET` | your value |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_RAZORPAY_KEY_ID` | your value |

